ific map or for more information, contact a reference librarian in the Geography & Map Division (202) 707-6277 or through the \"Ask a librarian\" link through the Geography & Map Division website https://ask.loc.gov/map-geography/. Title supplied by cataloger. Maps in this collection that may be in copyright are not available online. Available also through the Library of Congress Web site as a raster image. HI-20-01 through HI-20-28."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-04-29T15:17:49.207Z", "group": ["gmd/multimap", "catalog-split-12", "catalog", "multimaps", "main-catalog-split-12"], "hassegments": true, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2022589358/", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:gmd:gmdtitlecolmaps:hi:-0:20:hi-020:hi-020-01-01/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:gmd:gmdtitlecolmaps:hi:-0:20:hi-020:hi-020-01-01/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=699&w=700", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:gmd:gmdtitlecolmaps:hi:-0:20:hi-020:hi-020-01-01/full/pct:25/0/default.jpg#h=1399&w=1400"], "index": 5, "language": ["english"], "location": ["honolulu", "hawaii", "united states"], "mime_type": ["image/tiff", "image/jpeg", "image/jp2"], "number": ["2025-06-07t11:32:23.300000", "2022589358", "2024-01-31t15:32:03", "sheet"], "online_format": ["image"], "original_format": ["map", "collection"], "other_title": ["Alternate supplied title: Hawaii title collection--drawer 20", "Alternate supplied title: Hawaii title collection--cities and towns Honolulu 1926-1958"], "partof": ["cultural landscapes", "catalog", "single sheet maps, title collection", "cities and towns", "geography and map division"], "score": 28.974358, "shelf_id": "G4384.H6 coll .M3 drawer 20", "site": ["catalog"], "subject": ["maps", "tourist maps", "landowners", "real property", "honolulu (hawaii)", "hawaii", "honolulu", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-04-29T15:25:27.891Z", "title": "[Maps of Hawaii--cities and to